araty acittāvaraṇaḥ &brvbar; cittāvaraṇanāstitvād atrasto viparyāsātikrānto niṣṭhanirvāṇaḥ &brvbar; tryadhvavyavasthitāḥ sarvabuddhāḥ praj&ntilde;āpāramitām āśrityānuttarāṃ samyaksambodhim abhisaṃbuddhāḥ &brvbar; tasmāj j&ntilde;ātavyaṃ praj&ntilde;āpāramitā mahāmantro mahavidyāmantro 'nuttaramantro 'samasamamantraḥ sarvaduḥkhapraśamanaḥ &brvbar; satyam amithyatvāt &brvbar; praj&ntilde;apāramitāyām ukto mantraḥ &brvbar; tadyathā gate gate pāragate pārasaṃgate bodhi svāhā &brvbar; iti praj&ntilde;āpāramitāhṛdayaṃ samāptam"}]}